00:03:32.050 --> 00:03:34.900
a nonprofit in honor of
her late daughter aimed

00:03:34.900 --> 00:03:38.620
at destigmatizing mental
illness and suicide,

00:03:38.620 --> 00:03:41.050
and heightening awareness
of the magnitude

00:03:41.050 --> 00:03:43.660
of suicide as a
global health crisis.

00:03:43.660 --> 00:03:47.170
Nicole, thank you for joining
us to share your story.

00:03:47.170 --> 00:03:48.324
Nicole Browning.

